CTRL_DEAD_BAND.Description: rc control dead band (for pitch, roll, and rudder control)

CTRL_DBAND_THRO.Description: rc control dead band (for throttle channel only)

CTRL_MIN_THROT.Description: minimum user throttle to activate motors

CTRL_MAX.Description: maximum control applied to motors +- throttle

MOT_FRAME.Description: used as hint for frame config GUI

NAV_CEILING.Description: m relative to home alt. Maximum altitude in alt/pos/mission/dvh modes

NAV_HDFRE_CHAN.Description: radio channel for heading-free mode; set to zero to disable

IMU_ROT.Description: degrees to rotate the IMU to align with the frame

SPVR_FS_RAD_ST1.Description: radio failsafe stage 1 action (0 = position hold)

SPVR_FS_RAD_ST2.Description: radio failsafe stage 2 action (0 = land, 1 = RTH, land, 2 = Ascend if needed, RTH, land)

SPVR_FS_ADD_ALT.Description: meters to add to home alt. for falisafe stg.2 action == 2

SIG_BEEP_PRT.Description: negative sign before port number when using a piezo speaker, no sign when using a piezo buzzer

SIG_PWM_PRT.Description: External PWM-controlled signaling port, 0 to disable
